        "execSummary":  "Gemini Spark\u0027s macOS launch and expanded third-party integrations mark a practical step toward enterprise-relevant ambient AI ΓÇö agents that live in the background and act across applications without user prompting. For enterprise technology leaders, Spark\u0027s integration with tools like Dropbox and Canva previews the agentic workflow patterns employees will expect in workplace AI before enterprise-grade versions arrive. The current limitation to Google AI Ultra subscribers in the US is a meaningful constraint, but the trajectory points toward organizational rollouts within 12-18 months. IT and security teams should begin evaluating credential delegation, data-access boundaries, and acceptable-use policies for persistent desktop AI agents now.",
